main event: Two unidentified round white lights were observed at Lincoln AFB, Nebraska on July 14, 1965.
interesting points: The first object was bright and dimmed out multiple times during the sighting,The second object was less bright and followed the first by about 5 minutes,The initial observer thought the first sighting was a meteor, but the light reappeared,Observation was done visually from the ground,There were two reliable observers, including a Colonel and Lieutenant Colonel.
